South African House-Price Inflation Moderates to 3.3%, Standard Bank Says

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-06-03T14:09:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/south-african-house-price-inflation-moderates-to-3-3-standard-bank-says.html
South African house-price inflation
eased to an annual 3.3 percent in May from 3.4 percent in the
previous month, Standard Bank Group Ltd. said.  Growth in the residential property market will probably
“track inflation, with zero or negligible growth in real
terms” in 2011, the Johannesburg-based lender said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  